<subSubSection pageId="358" pageNumber="359" type="distribution">
<paragraph pageId="358" pageNumber="359">Distribution.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="358" pageNumber="359">
This species ranges from southern New Brunswick (Webster and Bousquet 2008: 16) to southwestern Wisconsin (Richland County, Peter W. Messer pers. comm. 2008), south to eastern Texas (Sabine County, Brian Raber pers. comm. 2010; Riley 2011) and central Florida (Peck and Thomas 1998: 18). The record from 
<normalizedToken originalValue="“Minnesota”">&quot;Minnesota&quot;</normalizedToken>
(Bousquet and Larochelle 1993: 126) needs confirmation.
</paragraph>
